{"tid":1097036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國雷神獲批$7000萬合約 台北部署愛國者系統","createTime":"2019-04-08T06:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T06:48:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"802e551d94e312d3712631b023eada74ada021dd","tid":1097036,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"美國國防部日前宣佈，美國軍火商雷神公司（Raytheon）已獲准簽訂價值近903.5萬美元（7,092萬港元）合約，在台北部署愛國者導彈防禦系統，並計劃在2024年4月3日前佈署完成。<br />\n<br />\n軍事新聞網站「Defense Blog」報道，自2015年1月起，在全球各地部署的愛國者導彈攔截系統已成功攔截逾百枚來襲導彈。雷神公司迄今已製造超過220枚愛國者導彈，並將其運送至16國客戶手中。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國之音報道，中國早在數年前開始流傳「中國反隱形雷達在北部沿海上空發現並鎖定了F-22隱形戰機」。此事一度被認為是宣傳，但去年12月24日，隱形雷達偵測專家、中國電子科技集團的科學家吳劍旗在一次演講中證實，中國使用米波雷達，可對F-22遠距跟蹤，只是一直存在低仰角盲區大、精確程度達不到引導火控雷達和戰鬥機對來襲目標進行攔截的缺陷。但這些缺陷很多已經被克服。<br />\n<br />\n美國《國家利益》周刊昨日轉載先前刊登過的文章指，先進雷達的確可以探測到美國的隱形戰機，因為隱形僅是延遲偵測與跟蹤的手段，尤其是在F-22隱形戰機外掛副油箱等狀態下更容易被米波雷達探測。<br />\n<br />\n文章特別提到，中國與俄羅斯正在加緊研製超高頻和特高頻（米波）雷達，對美國隱形戰機進行偵測，但否能鎖定目標並引導導彈進行攻擊，還有待觀察。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190408/59461905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59461905&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=a4d8c08d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59461905&h=dc3fba1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190408/59461905</a>"},{"pid":"d87062185f2fca85426d8e4d22b4a3e20cc31052","tid":1097036,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721e50d458f71946657e69caee5bd10f0f444e4f","tid":1097036,"uid":13010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"原來十六個國家分得二百幾枝咁少？<br />\n<br />\n咁唔計飽和轟炸，如果一次射三十枝導彈，點頂？"},{"pid":"3676e7cc56882aa23010d9786298c661e35738c3","tid":1097036,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:42:35.000Z","msg":"Thor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e54d3b57a2516f7dbf6a575a15044febd95b7a0","tid":1097036,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://phycat.files.wordpress.com/2018/05/b79416184b360c96b8fb9cf8404a7482-768x317.jpg?w=768\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphycat.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F05%2Fb79416184b360c96b8fb9cf8404a7482-768x317.jpg%3Fw%3D768&h=17de77eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"135b49c23476c82fc06bf444a13b6784efb40246","tid":1097036,"uid":13010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"721e50d458f71946657e69caee5bd10f0f444e4f","tid":1097036,"uid":13010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"原來十六個國家分得二百幾枝咁少？<br />\n<br />\n咁唔計飽和轟炸，如果一次射三十枝導彈，點頂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"睇返佢英文篇文，係more than 220 Patriot fire units，即係超過220 套發射系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係本身都起碼880枝，另外再搵資料，飛彈係做左過萬枝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://defence-blog.com/army/raytheon-awarded-9m-for-support-for-taiwans-patriot-missile-system.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdefence-blog.com%2Farmy%2Fraytheon-awarded-9m-for-support-for-taiwans-patriot-missile-system.html&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=f4fc500e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://defence-blog.com/army/raytheon-awarded-9m-for-support-for-taiwans-patriot-missile-system.html</a>"}]}